reviews.review_text: Great Show/Recording However this copy has Crazy>Playin'>Drums>Space on one song slot. The minute or so before the Gimme Some in Space is good and should be part of GSL (or Space as a stand alone). Also the Eyes is near 15 minutes long with a great intro. Regarded as one of the finest of the era. Last, not sure about the "fillers" at the end. Sound quality for an audience is very nice and with the BS LIE! thing in the first set it will always be a significant show worth having.
